title: Crystal Jade
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The owners of this Chinese restaurant are accommodating toward vegan and vegetarian diners and offer a complete vegetarian/vegan menu - ask for it. All items that can be made veg from the main menu can also be made to order. Wednesday is vegan night where it's 1/2 price vegan appetizers like fried rolls, curry puff, curry noodle soup, tofu steak, and spring rolls. Protein options include tofu and mock duck. AUG 2014 per owner, trying to sell and retire.
